text: Travis Wayne Childers (born March 29, 1958 in Booneville, Mississippi, United States) is an American politician. He represented Mississippi's 1st district in the U.S. House of Representatives from the May 2008 special election until 2011.Clarion Ledger: Childers wins 1st District for Democrats Childers did not win re-election in on November 2, 2010, he was defeated by former state senator Alan Nunnelee. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official Campaign Website *The Online Office of Congressman Travis Childers Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Mississippi Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
